    {"slug": "wei-zheng", "name": "魏征", "primaryRole": "minister", "roles": ["minister"], "importance": 85, "birthYear": 580, "deathYear": 643, "aliases": ["魏郑公"], "summary": "唐太宗名臣，以直谏著称。太宗称其为「人镜」，是贞观之治的重要功臣。"},
